docs.lead_paragraph: LEAD: OFFICIALS at the two county health departments on Long Island say that new Federal regulations prohibiting any mention of abortion in clinics that receive Federal funds will discriminate against poor women, interfere with their right to manage their pregnancies and hamper doctors and counselers.
